              <a href="tel:513-555-0123" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Now</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Services Overview -->
      <section class="services-overview">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Fairfield Floor Coating Specialists</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">
            Queen City Surface Coatings brings Butler County's most trusted floor coating expertise 
            directly to your Fairfield property. Our family-owned business understands the unique 
            climate challenges and architectural styles throughout the Fairfield community.
          </p>
          
          <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
              <div class="service-icon">üè†</div>
              <h3>Residential Garage Floors</h3>
              <p>Transform your Fairfield home's garage with durable epoxy coatings that withstand Ohio's harsh winters and humid summers.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Slip-resistant decorative flakes</li>
                <li>Chemical and stain resistant</li>
                <li>Easy maintenance and cleaning</li>
                <li>Custom color options</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
              <h3>Commercial & Industrial</h3>
              <p>Serving Fairfield's growing business district with heavy-duty coating solutions for warehouses, retail spaces, and manufacturing facilities.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>High-traffic durability</li>
                <li>Chemical resistance for industrial use</li>
                <li>Safety compliance features</li>
                <li>Minimal downtime installation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-card">
              <h3>Basement Waterproofing</h3>
              <p>Protect your Fairfield basement from moisture with our specialized basement floor coating systems.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Moisture barrier protection</li>
                <li>Mold and mildew prevention</li>
                <li>Temperature regulation</li>
                <li>Finished basement enhancement</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Local Expertise -->
      <section class="local-expertise">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="content-columns">
            <div class="content-column">
              <h2>Why Choose Us for Your Fairfield Floor Coating Project?</h2>
              
              <h3>Local Butler County Knowledge</h3>
              <p>
                Based in nearby Milford, we've been serving the Fairfield community for over 15 years. 
                We understand the specific challenges that Butler County's clay soil conditions and 
                seasonal weather patterns present for concrete flooring applications.
              </p>
              
              <h3>Climate-Specific Solutions</h3>
              <p>
                Fairfield's continental climate, with temperature swings from below freezing in winter 
                to 85¬∞F+ summers, demands floor coatings that can expand and contract without cracking. 
                Our polyaspartic and epoxy systems are specifically formulated for Ohio's climate extremes.
              </p>
              
              <h3>Community Partnerships</h3>
              <p>
                We're proud partners with several Fairfield businesses and have worked extensively 
                throughout the Village Green area, Fairfield Commons, and the historic downtown district. 
                Our local reputation is built on quality workmanship and exceptional customer service.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-column">
              <h3>Recent Fairfield Projects</h3>
              
              <div class="project-highlight">
                <h4>Fairfield Commons Area Residence</h4>
                <p>
                  <strong>Challenge:</strong> 3-car garage with severe oil staining and concrete spalling from road salt damage.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Solution:</strong> Complete concrete restoration with decorative metallic epoxy system 
                  featuring bronze and copper tones to complement the home's brick exterior.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Result:</strong> "The garage now looks better than our kitchen! The metallic finish 
                  catches the light beautifully and cleanup is incredibly easy." - Sarah M., Fairfield
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="project-highlight">
                <h4>Village Green District Basement</h4>
                <p>
                  <strong>Challenge:</strong> Finished basement with moisture infiltration issues affecting 
                  the concrete slab in this established Fairfield neighborhood.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Solution:</strong> Moisture mitigation system with vapor barrier epoxy coating 
                  and decorative quartz broadcasting for texture and slip resistance.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <strong>Result:</strong> Complete moisture control with an attractive, durable surface 
                  that transformed the basement into usable living space.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Technical Expertise -->
      <section class="technical-section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Advanced Floor Coating Systems for Fairfield Properties</h2>
          
          <div class="tech-grid">
            <div class="tech-item">
              <h3>Polyaspartic Coatings</h3>
              <p>
                Our premium polyaspartic systems are ideal for Fairfield's climate variations. 
                These advanced coatings cure quickly even in Butler County's humid conditions 
                and provide superior UV resistance for areas with natural light exposure.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Fast cure times (ready in 24 hours)</li>
                <li>Superior chemical resistance</li>
                <li>Temperature stability (-40¬∞F to 200¬∞F)</li>
                <li>Won't yellow or fade over time</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tech-item">
              <h3>100% Solids Epoxy Systems</h3>
              <p>
                Perfect for Fairfield basements and garages, our solvent-free epoxy systems 
                create a seamless, non-porous surface that's ideal for Ohio's moisture challenges.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Zero VOC emissions</li>
                <li>Maximum durability and longevity</li>
                <li>Chemical and abrasion resistance</li>
                <li>Custom decorative options</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tech-item">
              <h3>Decorative Concrete Systems</h3>
              <p>
                Transform plain concrete into stunning decorative surfaces with our 
                metallic epoxy, quartz broadcasting, and color flake systems.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Unlimited color combinations</li>
                <li>Metallic and pearlescent effects</li>
                <li>Slip-resistant textures</li>
                <li>Seamless, easy-clean surfaces</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Local Testimonials -->
      <section class="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>What Fairfield Customers Say</h2>
          
          <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Living near Harbin Park, we needed something that could handle muddy shoes 
                  and sporting equipment. The epoxy coating has been perfect - easy to clean 
                  and still looks new after 3 years!"
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Mike R.</strong> - Fairfield Homeowner
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Queen City Surface Coatings transformed our basement after water issues. 
                  The vapor barrier coating solved our moisture problems and looks fantastic. 
                  Professional work from start to finish."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Jennifer L.</strong> - Village Green Resident
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "As a Fairfield business owner, downtime costs money. They worked around 
                  our schedule and completed the warehouse floor coating over a weekend. 
                  Excellent service and durability."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Robert K.</strong> - Fairfield Business Owner
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Process & Quality -->
      <section class="process-section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Our Fairfield Floor Coating Process</h2>
          
          <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Property Assessment</h3>
                <p>
                  We evaluate your Fairfield property's specific conditions, including concrete age, 
                  moisture levels, and intended use to recommend the optimal coating system.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Surface Preparation</h3>
                <p>
                  Using diamond grinding and shot blasting techniques, we prepare the concrete 
                  surface for maximum adhesion and longevity of your floor coating system.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Professional Application</h3>
                <p>
                  Our certified technicians apply your chosen coating system using professional-grade 
                  equipment and techniques developed through years of Butler County experience.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">4</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Quality Inspection</h3>
                <p>
                  Every Fairfield installation includes thorough quality control checks and 
                  a comprehensive walkthrough to ensure your complete satisfaction.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Local Information -->
      <section class="local-info">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Serving Fairfield and Surrounding Butler County Communities</h2>
          
          <div class="info-columns">
            <div class="info-column">
              <h3>Service Areas</h3>
              <p>
                From our Milford base, we provide comprehensive floor coating services 
                throughout Fairfield and the greater Butler County region:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Fairfield proper and surrounding subdivisions</li>
                <li>Village Green and historic downtown district</li>
                <li>Fairfield Commons and commercial areas</li>
                <li>Harbin Park and recreational facility vicinity</li>
                <li>Industrial corridor along Pleasant Avenue</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-column">
              <h3>Local Building Considerations</h3>
              <p>
                We understand Fairfield's construction patterns and environmental factors:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Soil Conditions:</strong> Butler County clay soil requires proper moisture management</li>
                <li><strong>Climate Factors:</strong> Seasonal freeze-thaw cycles demand flexible coating systems</li>
                <li><strong>Home Styles:</strong> Ranch and colonial homes with attached garages are common</li>
                <li><strong>Age Considerations:</strong> Many 1970s-1990s homes need concrete restoration</li>
                <li><strong>Commercial Needs:</strong> Growing business district requires durable commercial solutions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="warranty-info">
            <h3>Comprehensive Warranty Coverage</h3>
            <p>
              Every Fairfield floor coating project includes our industry-leading warranty protection:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Lifetime warranty against delamination and adhesion failure</li>
              <li>5-year warranty against normal wear and weathering</li>
              <li>1-year warranty against manufacturing defects</li>
              <li>Free annual maintenance inspections</li>
              <li>Emergency repair services for covered issues</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Environmental Benefits -->
      <section class="environmental-section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Environmentally Responsible Floor Coatings</h2>
          
          <div class="env-content">
            <div class="env-column">
              <h3>Eco-Friendly Solutions</h3>
              <p>
                Queen City Surface Coatings is committed to environmental responsibility 
                in all our Fairfield installations:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Zero VOC epoxy and polyaspartic systems</li>
                <li>Sustainable concrete restoration vs. replacement</li>
                <li>Energy-efficient surface properties</li>
                <li>Reduced maintenance chemical requirements</li>
                <li>Long-lasting durability reduces waste</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="env-column">
              <h3>Energy Efficiency Benefits</h3>
              <p>
                Our floor coatings contribute to your Fairfield property's energy efficiency:
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Light-reflective surfaces reduce lighting needs</li>
                <li>Thermal mass optimization for temperature control</li>
                <li>Moisture barrier properties prevent energy loss</li>
                <li>Reduced heating/cooling in coated spaces</li>
                <li>LEED-compliant material options available</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="contact-content">
            <div class="contact-info">
              <h2>Ready to Transform Your Fairfield Floors?</h2>
              <p>
                Contact Queen City Surface Coatings today for your free estimate. 
                We're proud to serve the Fairfield community with premium floor coating solutions.
              </p>
              
              <div class="contact-details">
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Phone:</strong> (513) 555-0123
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Email:</strong> info@queencitysurface.com
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Service Area:</strong> Fairfield, OH and all of Butler County
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Business Hours:</strong> Monday-Saturday 7AM-7PM
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="service-promise">
                <h3>Our Promise to Fairfield Customers</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Free, no-obligation estimates</li>
                  <li>Transparent, competitive pricing</li>
                  <li>Professional, licensed, and insured</li>
                  <li>Lifetime warranty on workmanship</li>
                  <li>Local Butler County expertise</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="contact-form">
              <ContactForm />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    
    <Footer 
      footerLists={footerLists}
      footerSocials={footerSocials}
      copyrightName={settings.name}
    >
      <Logo slot="logo" />
    </Footer>
    
